Title: The Gorka Doe
Descriptions:
Howdy, Partner! You got that Buck pelt for me? Ah, there it is… Just a doggone minute there… You sure this is the Vyshnoye Buck? You didn't just bag the first buck you saw, now did ya’? Okay, I'll take yer word for it.

Anywho, the next pelt I need is The Kabanino Doe.

This beauty has been runnin’ ‘round like she's the Queen o’ Sheba, or some such.

Bring me her pelt and I'll pay you ₽2500.

Straight shots, Partner!
Travel to watering hole
Acquire pristine doe pelt
Travel to watering hole
Acquire pristine doe pelt
ObjectiveText: Travel to Kabinino and bag The Kabinino Doe’s pelt in pristine condition
